<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Fintech and energy remain king</h2>



<p>Investors are still doubling down on financial services and sustainable infrastructure.</p>



<p>Fintech attracted $221M, while the Energy &amp; Water sector secured $141M to solve the continent&#8217;s power gaps.</p>



<p>Logistics and Transport followed closely behind with $149M in total investment.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-large is-resized"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="819" height="1024" 
