<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>Hot: A wave of M&amp;A activity</strong></h2>



<p>The &#8220;exit&#8221; story is heating up with over 30 M&amp;A deals tracked this quarter.</p>



<p>Notable moves include Flutterwave&#8217;s acquisition of Mono and Moniepoint’s aggressive expansion into Kenya via Sumac Microfinance Bank.</p>



<p>These deals show that larger players are now buying their way into new markets and product lines.</p>



